name: Northwest Wild Foods
overview: Northwest Wild Foods provides wild gourmet foods from the Pacific Northwest to customers across the nation. They are a small family run company that specializing in providing quality wild products to retail and wholeale customers. They harvest wild red huckleberries, wild blue huckleberries, wild mtn. blackberries, wild mountain blueberries, wild salmonberries, wild black raspberries. Domestic berries they harvest include lingonberries, currants, and other hard to find berries out of europe. They recently started carrrying free range buffalo, wild mushrooms, and wild smoked seafood. Their berries also go into making gourmet jams, jellies and syrups.
